data.description: One level living on a large lot awaits new owners. With an ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 2.99% for part of the purchase price, buyers can take advantage of a lower potential payment. This three bedroom, three bath brick ranch home has been well maintained. With both a partial basement and detached garage, in addition to a bonus room and office, there is plenty of space. Multiple sun rooms add natural light and views of the well maintained grounds.  Recent upgrades include a new roof in 2021, crawlspace encapsulation in 2022 and over 7k of bathroom upgrades (to make ADA friendly), new water heater and sump pump in 2023. You must come see this home to truly appreciate the potential it has to offer.
